{"id": "1454683620978462863", "channel_id": "1454683620978462863", "type": 0, "author_id": "183782216353054720", "author_name": "omnichromia", "author_bot": false, "content": "I know this is awkward timing considering the \"Everyone Look at Reproduction Frenzy!!!!\" event just ended lol, but I was having a conversation about this recently and wanted to bring it up. I haven't yet read any of the Frenzy stories myself (aside from Ramona) so I can't speak myself on their contents, but I know aside from some notable exceptions they're entirely SFW on average.\n\nThe original CN (繁衍狂热) does literally translate to \"Reproduction Frenzy\" but it just doesn't seem to me like an accurate description for the contents of the stories. \n\nFrom what I understand, the stories are about a strange mass hysteria/mass psychogenic illness phenomenon, affecting Awakeners and spurred on by the Remouahe event, the main symptoms of which being heightened libido, a low fever(?) and/or lowered inhibitions.\n\n## <@1376763322568937562> would it be within reason to give a new name to this section of content at this point?\nIf so, I have some ideas that we can use as a starting point for brainstorming;\n\nI feel like a good direction to look is the idea of being \"in heat\", and the other thought is—as funny as it is—technically \"hysteria\" is a pretty apt term here despite its well-deserved antiquation. <:karen_nervous:1408324291237511259> At the very least, \"Reproduction Frenzy\" still sounds a little stilted, and I think \"Intimacy\" is probably a better descriptor than \"Reproduction\".\n\nHeat of Remouahe?\nMass Heat Hysteria?\nIntimacy Fever?\nHeat Wave Frenzy?\nHeat-Wave Hysteria?\nIntimacy Episode?\nIntimate Anecdotes?", "timestamp": "2025-12-28T03:53:21.956000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-12-28T03:54:30.583000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1376763322568937562"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1454683621649682542", "filename": "Screenshot_20251227-112128.png", "content_type": "image/webp", "size": 461710, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1454683620978462863/1454683621649682542/Screenshot_20251227-112128.png?ex=6a321a32&is=6a30c8b2&hm=1ad4838f5264ee5c1f20b7585442c06f882f47e93abd99cda8a63f28856cd9bf&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1454683620978462863", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "\"Reproduction Frenzy\"?", "forum_channel_id": "1404748432328888401", "thread_tags": ["1404748529724952576", "1410391772894330961"], "is_thread_starter": true}
